  "description": null
 },
 "html": "<p>Our trees are carrying a heavy load this time of year.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-093.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1628\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 093\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-093-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>  With the cold weather on us, I decided to whip up a lemon pudding.  Little effort for lots of deliciousness.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-092.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1615\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 092\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-092-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>YOU NEED:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>80 g butter, melted</li>\n<li>210 castor sugar<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-062.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1616\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 062\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-062-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>4 eggs – separate the eggs<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-064.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1618\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 064\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-064-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>500 ml milk</li>\n<li>40 g cake flour<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-068.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1619\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 068\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-068-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>30 ml finely grated lemon zest<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-071.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1620\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 071\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-071-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOW:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>whisk the melted butter, lemon zest, flour, egg yolks and 125 ml of the castor sugar in a bowl</li>\n<li>slowly whisk in the milk<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-078.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1622\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 078\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-078-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>whisk the egg whites to soft peaks and now slowly add the remaining sugar to the egg whites – now you need to whisk well until it becomes glossy<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-076.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1621\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 076\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-076-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>slowly fold your egg white mixture into your egg yolk mixture – work gently</li>\n<li>pour everything into a greased oven dish<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-083.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1629\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 083\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-083-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>place the dish in a larger pan with water<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-087.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1623\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 087\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-087-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>bake for 45 minutes at 180 degrees Celsius<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-102.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1624\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 102\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-102-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>We enjoyed the pudding with mascarpone cheese. Cream is just as lovely.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-1071.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1627\" alt=\"SUURLEMOENPOEDING BLOG 107\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/SUURLEMOENPOEDING-BLOG-1071-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
 "recipe": null
}
